==Description==

A rabbibunny who taxi's citizens around Citadel Island for a small fare.

==Role in Twinsen's adventure==

A character who is just there if you can't be bothered to walk somewhere far on Citidel Island.
He only drives his scooter though when it is sunny.
Although when it is raining on Citidal Island he tells you that you can run and jump.

